<node TEXT="INTERMITTENT FASTING - Should I do Intermittent Fasting? " FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1230936846" CREATED="1610200453144" MODIFIED="1612192668238" LINK="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u84Gh9pzftY">
<node TEXT="What is Intermittent fasting?" ID="ID_1339472185" CREATED="1612189914649" MODIFIED="1612189914649">
<node TEXT="First of all,intermittent fasting is not a diet but a dieting pattern in which there is a window where you can eat and there is a window where you have to fast." ID="ID_591795733" CREATED="1612189914651" MODIFIED="1612189914651"/>
<node TEXT="Now, there are a lot of versions of intermittent fasting but the most common and the practiced one is the 16-8 method." ID="ID_764137725" CREATED="1612189914656" MODIFIED="1612189914656"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="How does intermittent fasting work?" ID="ID_1183425987" CREATED="1612189914660" MODIFIED="1612189914660">
<node TEXT="Intermittent fasting acts as a shock for your body." ID="ID_156208393" CREATED="1612189914662" MODIFIED="1612189914662"/>
<node TEXT="When you do intermittent fasting, there are a lot of hormonal changes in the body which help you effectively lose body fat." ID="ID_1362201539" CREATED="1612189914663" MODIFIED="1612189914663"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="What are the advantages of intermittent fasting?" ID="ID_1258654419" CREATED="1612189914667" MODIFIED="1612189914667">
<node TEXT="it drops the insulin level." ID="ID_501792601" CREATED="1612189914669" MODIFIED="1612189914669"/>
<node TEXT="intermittent fasting is known to increase your human growth hormone by as much as 5 times" ID="ID_1622861814" CREATED="1612189914671" MODIFIED="1612189914671"/>
<node TEXT="it increases your metabolism" ID="ID_1224356380" CREATED="1612189914672" MODIFIED="1612189914672"/>
<node TEXT="it can keep you away from diseases like type 2 diabetes, heart disease, Alzheimer’s disease and even cancer." ID="ID_1568257059" CREATED="1612189914673" MODIFIED="1612189914673"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="What are the side effects of intermittent fasting?" ID="ID_73361388" CREATED="1612189914676" MODIFIED="1612189914676">
<node TEXT="First of all you have to keep a fast for 16 hours" ID="ID_157153882" CREATED="1612189914677" MODIFIED="1612189914677"/>
<node TEXT="because you are allowed to have black coffee in your fasting period, people tend to go overboard with it. This in the long run can be harmful." ID="ID_425727141" CREATED="1612189914678" MODIFIED="1612189914678"/>
<node TEXT="One major problem which people generally face in IF is that they get obsessed with food" ID="ID_360545648" CREATED="1612189914681" MODIFIED="1612189914681"/>
<node TEXT="another side effect of IF could be lack of sleep." ID="ID_1842259826" CREATED="1612189914682" MODIFIED="1612189914682"/>
<node TEXT="Now overeating is also one problem which people generally face in IF." ID="ID_1306368696" CREATED="1612189914683" MODIFIED="1612189914683"/>
<node TEXT="some people may also face fatigue or lower energy levels" ID="ID_1979876287" CREATED="1612189914684" MODIFIED="1612189914684"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="How you should eat in Intermittent fasting?" ID="ID_1174116198" CREATED="1612189914684" MODIFIED="1612189914684">
<node TEXT="break your fast with fruits." ID="ID_1599932193" CREATED="1612189914685" MODIFIED="1612189914685"/>
<node TEXT="Then in the 8 hour window, have 3-4 meals." ID="ID_113900293" CREATED="1612189914686" MODIFIED="1612189914686"/>
<node TEXT="Keep your meals high in protein, well balanced with complex carbohydrates, healthy fats, vitamins and minerals" ID="ID_1999148133" CREATED="1612189914687" MODIFIED="1612189914687"/>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="SKINNY FAT SOLUTION - How I got RIPPED? " FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1489854291" CREATED="1610200453144" MODIFIED="1612192667566" LINK="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VaboFpYAu88">
<node TEXT="  The skinny fat solution boils down to three  basic factors.   Workout, Nutrition and Sleep.   " ID="ID_975328588" CREATED="1612190432208" MODIFIED="1612190447247"/>
<node TEXT="workout" ID="ID_207711807" CREATED="1612190452135" MODIFIED="1612190453363">
<node TEXT="  Your focus should be on weight training and  not cardio. " ID="ID_1452893303" CREATED="1612190463716" MODIFIED="1612190464693"/>
<node TEXT="any form of resistance  training is very important to increase the   muscle mass.  " ID="ID_468553309" CREATED="1612190469520" MODIFIED="1612190470235"/>
<node TEXT="workout for 5 days  and keep a rest for 2 days. " ID="ID_352554842" CREATED="1612190473586" MODIFIED="1612190474755"/>
<node TEXT="  In all those 5 days you should train one muscle  group in a day. " ID="ID_1082772487" CREATED="1612190477773" MODIFIED="1612190478861"/>
<node TEXT="  Now your workout time should range from 45  minutes to maximum 60 minutes. " ID="ID_93261147" CREATED="1612190481877" MODIFIED="1612190483016"/>
<node TEXT="  Also try to lift heavy weights.  Now, when I say heavy, I mean heavy according  to your strength. " ID="ID_1902678582" CREATED="1612190488245" MODIFIED="1612190489193"/>
<node TEXT="  Also week by week try to increase the weight. " ID="ID_1058272739" CREATED="1612190494095" MODIFIED="1612190494975"/>
<node TEXT="  On any particular day you can do 5-6 exercises  of one muscle group. " ID="ID_1449400017" CREATED="1612190499006" MODIFIED="1612190501134"/>
<node TEXT="  Do 3 sets of each exercise.  The rep ranges could be 12,10 and 8. " ID="ID_785108298" CREATED="1612190504306" MODIFIED="1612190505560"/>
<node TEXT="you should not do too much of cardio. keep your cardio training  twice a week. " ID="ID_1093439435" CREATED="1612190513495" MODIFIED="1612190514299"/>
<node TEXT="  Also your cardio training should not be more  than 5 to 10 minutes.   " ID="ID_1463219475" CREATED="1612190518818" MODIFIED="1612190519627"/>
<node TEXT="your abs training should be short  but rigorous. " ID="ID_443364073" CREATED="1612190523840" MODIFIED="1612190524696"/>
<node TEXT="So after the weight training session, you can keep your abs training to 5 to 10 minutes. " ID="ID_1585436959" CREATED="1612190528503" MODIFIED="1612190532884"/>
<node TEXT="So you can structure your workout in such  a way that on monday you do abs, tuesday sprinting,  wednesday again abs, Thursday again abs and friday again abs.    " ID="ID_216356090" CREATED="1612190540499" MODIFIED="1612190543302"/>
