<node TEXT="So after I&apos;m done with my day, I normally go out on my balcony, but I simply stay under moonlight for some time. Moon helps me relieve the stress of our dieting" ID="ID_797657168" CREATED="1611556594571" MODIFIED="1611556594571"/>
<node TEXT="Next thing that I do is I go to the kitchen and have the milk, warm milk and properties, which helps you calm down." ID="ID_1544261647" CREATED="1611556594601" MODIFIED="1611556594601">
<node TEXT="I keep on changing the way I prepare depending upon my mood and season." ID="ID_316320184" CREATED="1611556594608" MODIFIED="1611556594608"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Then I go to my bedroom where the first thing that I do is set the tone for a deep sleep by inducing some fragrance." ID="ID_539483998" CREATED="1611556594609" MODIFIED="1611556594609">
<node TEXT="I use an essential oil diffuser, which I feel with almost 90 percent water and then five to six drops off." ID="ID_1828582062" CREATED="1611556594616" MODIFIED="1611556594616"/>
<node TEXT="In this light, it creates an aromatic atmosphere within ten minutes." ID="ID_9467994" CREATED="1611556594618" MODIFIED="1611556594618"/>
<node TEXT="Sandalwood and jasmine are some essential oils, especially recommended for inducing sweet aromatherapy" ID="ID_777906497" CREATED="1611556594619" MODIFIED="1611556594619"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="After slowly finishing them milk, my hand reaches out to my dairy." ID="ID_1776285311" CREATED="1611556594630" MODIFIED="1611556594630">
<node TEXT="I spend just about five to ten minutes writing something, maybe an experience that I feel is worth remembering." ID="ID_1173654698" CREATED="1611556594630" MODIFIED="1611556594630"/>
<node TEXT="Any insight that I might have had on that particular day, or even every idea I scribble just about anything that&apos;s on my mind." ID="ID_82759784" CREATED="1611556594634" MODIFIED="1611556594634"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Then I read something light. Like these days I&apos;m reading If Truth Be Told Amongst My Mind, written by Swannee." ID="ID_1584316442" CREATED="1611556594639" MODIFIED="1611556594639">
<node TEXT="Reading a book like this before sleeping comes my mind and also instills my subconscious with profound spiritual thoughts." ID="ID_239290135" CREATED="1611556594643" MODIFIED="1611556594643"/>
<node TEXT="I spend about fifteen to thirty minutes depending on the day." ID="ID_719674898" CREATED="1611556594647" MODIFIED="1611556594647"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Next thing that I do is I go to the washroom and wash my face." ID="ID_364477027" CREATED="1611556594648" MODIFIED="1611556594648">
<node TEXT="I feel my mouth full with water and splash water on the eyes as it relaxes them almost instantly." ID="ID_804618420" CREATED="1611556594649" MODIFIED="1611556594649"/>
<node TEXT="This I clean my teeth using food powder and scrape my tongue and then I also wash my feet." ID="ID_202762206" CREATED="1611556594651" MODIFIED="1611556594651"/>
<node TEXT="It eases of the whole body just like that, when this trip can be a little intimidating during winters, but it&apos;s worth doing." ID="ID_816276131" CREATED="1611556594652" MODIFIED="1611556594652"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Then after drying my feet with a towel, I take some sesame oil and massage them for a couple of minutes." ID="ID_550941262" CREATED="1611556594656" MODIFIED="1611556594656">
<node TEXT="You might be amazed to know that your feet has some points that are connected to your head." ID="ID_758609967" CREATED="1611556594657" MODIFIED="1611556594657"/>
<node TEXT="When you massage them, you feel light and sleepy. Don&apos;t believe me. Try getting acupressure foot massage." ID="ID_1107978568" CREATED="1611556594659" MODIFIED="1611556594659"/>
<node TEXT="Someday you might actually doze off in between the massage." ID="ID_1368082836" CREATED="1611556594663" MODIFIED="1611556594663"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Then I light a lamp" ID="ID_962202423" CREATED="1611556594663" MODIFIED="1611556594663">
<node TEXT="I turn all lights off. Except of course the oil lamp I then practice is a yogic purification technique that involves standing." ID="ID_164853056" CREATED="1611556594664" MODIFIED="1611556594664"/>
<node TEXT="At one point in my case, the flame of the lamp." ID="ID_1590579138" CREATED="1611556594668" MODIFIED="1611556594668"/>
<node TEXT="It increases concentration ability, strengthens the eyes and has some other amazing benefits." ID="ID_1374919755" CREATED="1611556594669" MODIFIED="1611556594669"/>
<node TEXT="I spend about five to ten minutes and then close my eyes to meditate." ID="ID_656987385" CREATED="1611556594669" MODIFIED="1611556594669"/>
<node TEXT="I try to remain aware of every inhalation and exhalation." ID="ID_23894830" CREATED="1611556594670" MODIFIED="1611556594670"/>
<node TEXT="I meditate for about twenty minutes, sometimes less and sometimes even more" ID="ID_1798420362" CREATED="1611556594670" MODIFIED="1611556594670"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="After meditating, I am almost ready to fall asleep." ID="ID_1231248947" CREATED="1611556594671" MODIFIED="1611556594671"/>
<node TEXT="Often I put a drop of Desi ghee in each of my eyes, especially on those days when I had been brainwashed." ID="ID_1466094763" CREATED="1611556594672" MODIFIED="1611556594672"/>
<node TEXT="I may even practice nausea by putting a drop of key or a medicinal oil like another long in each of my nostrils." ID="ID_933765879" CREATED="1611556594673" MODIFIED="1611556594673"/>
<node TEXT="On a few days I skip this step altogether, then practicing affirmations for about a couple of minutes in my mind," ID="ID_739187755" CREATED="1611556594677" MODIFIED="1611556594677">
<node TEXT="feeding my subconscious with positive thoughts and with a slight awareness of my breath." ID="ID_1071486885" CREATED="1611556594680" MODIFIED="1611556594680"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="I doze off almost instantly with my head pointed in the aesthetic." ID="ID_670947753" CREATED="1611556594682" MODIFIED="1611556594682"/>
<node TEXT="I sleep on the left side as it helps digest the food better, this holistic routine not only induces deep sleep faster," ID="ID_1116392591" CREATED="1611556594683" MODIFIED="1611556594683">
<node TEXT="but more importantly, when I wake up the next day, I feel fresh and energetic." ID="ID_615374228" CREATED="1611556594686" MODIFIED="1611556594686"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="I admit that there are days in my life when I&apos;m not able to follow it completely, but that&apos;s OK." ID="ID_1969577475" CREATED="1611556594687" MODIFIED="1611556594687"/>
</node>
</node>
