<node TEXT="Category1 includes some feasts dark fantasy, parlay, Milano audio Hide and Seek bought one and all other dream biscuits." ID="ID_34792042" CREATED="1611562384642" MODIFIED="1611562384642">
<node TEXT="These may be your favorite biscuits but you should know that they also are unhealthy." ID="ID_680416435" CREATED="1611562384657" MODIFIED="1611562384657"/>
<node TEXT="First of all, if we go through the nutritional information of oreo biscuits per 100 grams, it has 70 grams of carbohydrates out of which 38.6 grams is just sugar that is close to 10 teaspoons of sugar." ID="ID_100495880" CREATED="1611562384658" MODIFIED="1611562384658"/>
<node TEXT="What is more alarming are their ingredients which include Refined Flour, hydrogenated oils, artificial colors, flavors, emulsifiers, enhancers, raising agents and whatnot." ID="ID_1086860379" CREATED="1611562384662" MODIFIED="1611562384662"/>
