<node TEXT="If healthy lifestyle is what you are looking for, then these biscuits should not be in your list." ID="ID_829983372" CREATED="1611562384668" MODIFIED="1611562384668"/>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Category2 is that of the biscuits which are better than the ones in category number one, but are nowhere close to the best most popular biscuits like Parle-g,tiger,Good day Mari Patanjali and others fall into this category." ID="ID_1101246910" CREATED="1611562384670" MODIFIED="1611562384670">
<node TEXT="The sugar content in them is between 20 to 30 grams per 100 grams, which is about five to eight teaspoons per 100 grams per kg has 25 grams of super good day biscuits have 22 grams of sugar." ID="ID_262559793" CREATED="1611562384673" MODIFIED="1611562384673"/>
<node TEXT="Britannia nice time has 30 grams of sugar and Mari biscuits have around 21 grams of sugar. Frankly, the sugar content in them is not a major issue." ID="ID_1487867268" CREATED="1611562384677" MODIFIED="1611562384677"/>
<node TEXT="What concerns me more is that they too are made from refined flours, refined oils, raising agents, artificial flavors and emulsifiers" ID="ID_1041978823" CREATED="1611562384680" MODIFIED="1611562384680"/>
<node TEXT="So these biscuits are not a healthy choice either." ID="ID_871956622" CREATED="1611562384683" MODIFIED="1611562384683"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Category3 includes Britannia neutrinoless biscuits, sunfest farmlet biscuits, old biscuits, whole wheat biscuits and other digestive cookies." ID="ID_536572554" CREATED="1611562384684" MODIFIED="1611562384684">
<node TEXT="Their name suggests that they are very healthy, but are they?" ID="ID_990486225" CREATED="1611562384689" MODIFIED="1611562384689"/>
<node TEXT="Let&apos;s see, first of all old cookies is just a marketing gimmick. sunfest maryline oats have only 1.5% oat flakes Nutri choice or cookies have only 6% oats." ID="ID_885847729" CREATED="1611562384690" MODIFIED="1611562384690"/>
<node TEXT="Similarly, only 10 multigrain biscuits also fall under the same umbrella because they do have high percentage of refined laws." ID="ID_1033148559" CREATED="1611562384692" MODIFIED="1611562384692"/>
<node TEXT="0% sugar is another marketing gimmick such biscuits may not have added white sugar but are loaded with artificial sweeteners and maltodextrin." ID="ID_1043220667" CREATED="1611562384695" MODIFIED="1611562384695"/>
<node TEXT="The companies too are aware of the harmful effects of the artificial sweeteners." ID="ID_1549311707" CREATED="1611562384698" MODIFIED="1611562384698"/>
<node TEXT="That is why these biscuits come with a warning not recommended for children." ID="ID_733917955" CREATED="1611562384699" MODIFIED="1611562384699"/>
<node TEXT="Although other digested cookies are still better than most biscuits in the market as they have at least some amount of whole grains." ID="ID_56258681" CREATED="1611562384699" MODIFIED="1611562384699"/>
<node TEXT="As a result these are comparatively high in fiber and protein one can consume two to three biscuits on a daily basis without worrying about any kind of health problems" ID="ID_526736010" CREATED="1611562384702" MODIFIED="1611562384702"/>
</node>
