<node TEXT="the   three major causes of hair fall and the ways to fix it " FOLDED="true" ID="ID_556969843" CREATED="1612013952562" MODIFIED="1612157336621">
<node TEXT="1 is poor blood circulation" ID="ID_1824543125" CREATED="1612013974763" MODIFIED="1612013984784">
<node TEXT="the nutrients in our body   flow through blood   if the blood circulation in your scalp   area is low even if you take a   nutritional diet your hair will fall  " ID="ID_1425387173" CREATED="1612013992896" MODIFIED="1612014003470"/>
<node TEXT="this   is because the nutrients are not able to   reach the scalp area  " ID="ID_250952260" CREATED="1612014010592" MODIFIED="1612014011623"/>
