<node TEXT="How to Boost Testosterone Naturally - 6 WAYS " FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1173852265" CREATED="1610200453145" MODIFIED="1612615963700" LINK="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rpj-O4Lk6QI">
<node TEXT="1 WAY - NUTRITION" ID="ID_248715723" CREATED="1612430022706" MODIFIED="1612430022706">
<node TEXT="The foods that we eat impact our hormones in a positive or a negative way." ID="ID_1631810799" CREATED="1612430022722" MODIFIED="1612430022722"/>
<node TEXT="Needless to say, one should maintain a balanced diet." ID="ID_1120009562" CREATED="1612430022722" MODIFIED="1612430022722"/>
<node TEXT="Specifically talking about testosterone, there are three ingredients that should be in your diet on a daily basis." ID="ID_1919337789" CREATED="1612430022722" MODIFIED="1612430022722"/>
<node TEXT="These are Zinc, Vitamin D and Fats." ID="ID_1421608208" CREATED="1612430022722" MODIFIED="1612430022722"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="2 WAY - EXERCISE" ID="ID_1359103533" CREATED="1612430022722" MODIFIED="1612430022722">
<node TEXT="The right type of exercise can have a dramatic effect on the production of testosterone." ID="ID_1456857815" CREATED="1612430022722" MODIFIED="1612430022722"/>
<node TEXT="Specially weight training, when done even 3 to 4 times a week can boost your testosterone levels considerably." ID="ID_937063858" CREATED="1612430022737" MODIFIED="1612430022737"/>
<node TEXT="Studies have suggested that the higher the intensity of workout is, the greater will the response of testosterone." ID="ID_1310697047" CREATED="1612430022737" MODIFIED="1612430022737"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="3 WAY - SLEEP" ID="ID_857279628" CREATED="1612430022737" MODIFIED="1612430022737">
<node TEXT="When it comes to sleep, it is always about quality and not quantity." ID="ID_1347636668" CREATED="1612430022737" MODIFIED="1612430022737"/>
<node TEXT="After you wake up in the morning from a good sound sleep, your test levels are at peak and slowly they drop by the evening." ID="ID_1915742599" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753"/>
<node TEXT="In order to have deep sleep, you can do two things." ID="ID_1900925954" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="4 WAY - REDUCE STRESS" ID="ID_1880689515" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753">
<node TEXT="When we are stressed out, our body produces a hormone called cortisol." ID="ID_1403221335" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753"/>
<node TEXT="Cortisol is inversely proportional to testosterone." ID="ID_1151639842" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753"/>
<node TEXT="That means the higher the level of cortisol in the body, the lower will be the testosterone." ID="ID_1928727147" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753"/>
<node TEXT="Apart from this, there are many disadvantages of having a high cortisol levels in the body." ID="ID_882269471" CREATED="1612430022753" MODIFIED="1612430022753"/>
<node TEXT="So one should make an effort to reduce the stress levels." ID="ID_634029145" CREATED="1612430022768" MODIFIED="1612430022768"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="5 WAY - AVOID SOME THINGS" ID="ID_891769344" CREATED="1612430022768" MODIFIED="1612430022768">
<node TEXT="Now, there are 3 things that you should avoid or keep them in moderation when it comes to boosting your testosterone levels." ID="ID_1724719583" CREATED="1612430022768" MODIFIED="1612430022768"/>
<node TEXT="All three effect the body in such a way that it starts producing less amount of testosterone." ID="ID_1575887347" CREATED="1612430022768" MODIFIED="1612430022768"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="6 WAY - LOSE WEIGHT" ID="ID_1740632299" CREATED="1612430022768" MODIFIED="1612430022768">
<node TEXT="If you are overweight, shedding a few kilos can increase your testosterone levels." ID="ID_182931629" CREATED="1612430022768" MODIFIED="1612430022768"/>
<node TEXT="According to studies, overweight men are more likely to have low testosterone levels." ID="ID_1829330615" CREATED="1612430022784" MODIFIED="1612430022784"/>
<node TEXT="So basically, if you follow the points that we have already discussed, you will be able to optimise your bodyweight." ID="ID_1684311625" CREATED="1612430022784" MODIFIED="1612430022784"/>
</node>
</node>
</node>
