</node>
<node TEXT="It has been scientifically proven that the  saliva in the morning is most powerful.  " ID="ID_1802779531" CREATED="1612035954901" MODIFIED="1612035983915"/>
<node TEXT="It can in itself cure many diseases." ID="ID_960675098" CREATED="1612035990514" MODIFIED="1612035993396"/>
