<node TEXT="INTERMITTENT FASTING - Should I do Intermittent Fasting? " FOLDED="true" ID="ID_131388771" CREATED="1610200453144" MODIFIED="1612192668238" LINK="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u84Gh9pzftY">
<node TEXT="What is Intermittent fasting?" ID="ID_1331356844" CREATED="1612189914649" MODIFIED="1612189914649">
<node TEXT="First of all,intermittent fasting is not a diet but a dieting pattern in which there is a window where you can eat and there is a window where you have to fast." ID="ID_1538918691" CREATED="1612189914651" MODIFIED="1612189914651"/>
<node TEXT="Now, there are a lot of versions of intermittent fasting but the most common and the practiced one is the 16-8 method." ID="ID_167735496" CREATED="1612189914656" MODIFIED="1612189914656"/>
