<node TEXT="WEIGHT LOSS MISTAKES - How to Lose Weight Fast? " FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1138468704" CREATED="1610200453144" MODIFIED="1612255612850" LINK="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BPHMxr51VQE">
<node TEXT="Weight Loss Mistake  1 -" ID="ID_270483525" CREATED="1612192661605" MODIFIED="1612192661605">
<node TEXT="Stop measuring your progress in Kgs and start measuring it in inches." ID="ID_1117215001" CREATED="1612192661607" MODIFIED="1612192661607"/>
<node TEXT="Suppose you start working out and after a few days you step on weighing scale and you see that you have not reduced even a single kg." ID="ID_106679991" CREATED="1612192661608" MODIFIED="1612192661608"/>
<node TEXT="Well, let that number not decide how well you are doing." ID="ID_1106920246" CREATED="1612192661612" MODIFIED="1612192661612"/>
<node TEXT="beause there are chances that you have lost fat and at the same time you have put on some muscle" ID="ID_1235396276" CREATED="1612192661613" MODIFIED="1612192661613"/>
<node TEXT="instead you should take a measuring tape and see if your waistline has reduced" ID="ID_338143037" CREATED="1612192661614" MODIFIED="1612192661614"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Weight Loss Mistake 2 -" ID="ID_1807151740" CREATED="1612192661615" MODIFIED="1612192661615">
<node TEXT="Doing wrong workout." ID="ID_1582591533" CREATED="1612192661615" MODIFIED="1612192661615"/>
<node TEXT="Most people think that doing cardio vascular exercise on a treadmill, running for long period of time will help them reduce a lot of weight." ID="ID_163218697" CREATED="1612192661617" MODIFIED="1612192661617"/>
<node TEXT="This is not true. Cardio training is great for heart health but it is not ideal for weight loss." ID="ID_442346173" CREATED="1612192661620" MODIFIED="1612192661620"/>
<node TEXT="high intensity cardio is where you train your body like a s sprinter and not like a marathon runner" ID="ID_1073631479" CREATED="1612192661621" MODIFIED="1612192661621"/>
<node TEXT="this type of work out will help you reduce weight 5 times faster than just running on it" ID="ID_520136071" CREATED="1612192661622" MODIFIED="1612192661622"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Weight Loss Mistake 3 -" ID="ID_513178165" CREATED="1612192661622" MODIFIED="1612192661622">
<node TEXT="Underestimating the calories." ID="ID_1428629091" CREATED="1612192661623" MODIFIED="1612192661623"/>
<node TEXT="In order to lose weight, a person should consume calories less than the maintenance calories." ID="ID_585382906" CREATED="1612192661624" MODIFIED="1612192661624"/>
<node TEXT="Everybody knows that. But what many people don’t know is that how many calories a particular food contains." ID="ID_1876260629" CREATED="1612192661625" MODIFIED="1612192661625"/>
<node TEXT="And in this process they end up under estimating the calories that they have consumed." ID="ID_208603336" CREATED="1612192661627" MODIFIED="1612192661627"/>
<node TEXT="A study shows that people tend of underestimate the calories by as much as 50%." ID="ID_370812133" CREATED="1612192661627" MODIFIED="1612192661627"/>
<node TEXT="track your calories for just 10 days" ID="ID_691053378" CREATED="1612192661628" MODIFIED="1612192661628"/>
<node TEXT="in this 10 days,you will have a rough idea as to how many calories a particular food can contain" ID="ID_1528445278" CREATED="1612192661629" MODIFIED="1612192661629"/>
<node TEXT="This is one of the major reasons why people fail to lose weight." ID="ID_686931156" CREATED="1612192661630" MODIFIED="1612192661630"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Weight Loss Mistake 4 -" ID="ID_1071785510" CREATED="1612192661630" MODIFIED="1612192661630">
<node TEXT="Overloading yourself." ID="ID_1918333488" CREATED="1612192661631" MODIFIED="1612192661631"/>
<node TEXT="Doing weight loss is not a one or two day process." ID="ID_248700009" CREATED="1612192661632" MODIFIED="1612192661632"/>
<node TEXT="It is a journey in itself. It demands you to change your various eating habits." ID="ID_542543344" CREATED="1612192661632" MODIFIED="1612192661632"/>
<node TEXT="Now, if you suddenly subject yourself to a hardcore diet and start working out along with it, there are high chances that you get frustrated in between and stop the journey altogether." ID="ID_1010869765" CREATED="1612192661633" MODIFIED="1612192661633"/>
<node TEXT="So, it is always better to take small steps." ID="ID_1020384913" CREATED="1612192661635" MODIFIED="1612192661635"/>
<node TEXT="first take care of your diet and then go for exercise" ID="ID_570146088" CREATED="1612192661636" MODIFIED="1612192661636"/>
<node TEXT="next,you can opt for healthy alternatives" ID="ID_25304920" CREATED="1612192661637" MODIFIED="1612192661637"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Weight Loss Mistake 5 -" ID="ID_127465183" CREATED="1612192661637" MODIFIED="1612192661637">
<node TEXT="Making it Uncomfortable" ID="ID_728490649" CREATED="1612192661638" MODIFIED="1612192661638"/>
<node TEXT="for many people the idea of a weight loss diet is starvation." ID="ID_368091186" CREATED="1612192661639" MODIFIED="1612192661639"/>
<node TEXT="People who skip their breakfast, lunch actually eat like a dinosaur in their dinner. Never make this mistake." ID="ID_507840936" CREATED="1612192661640" MODIFIED="1612192661640"/>
<node TEXT="This is simply because starvation is not sustainable. Nor is it healthy." ID="ID_35462127" CREATED="1612192661640" MODIFIED="1612192661640"/>
<node TEXT="Similarly, some people after working out will take the liberty and pamper themselves with delicious food outside." ID="ID_1409008377" CREATED="1612192661641" MODIFIED="1612192661641"/>
<node TEXT="This happens because they have put themselves into uncomfortable position which are not sustainable for long. Never do this mistake." ID="ID_450833899" CREATED="1612192661643" MODIFIED="1612192661643"/>
<node TEXT="all you need to do is eat the right food in right quantities" ID="ID_804281761" CREATED="1612192661645" MODIFIED="1612192661645"/>
</node>
</node>
